Package com.northeastern.labyrinth.Remote

Class ProxyPlayer

java.lang.Object
com.northeastern.labyrinth.Remote.ProxyPlayer
All Implemented Interfaces:
IPlayer
public class ProxyPlayer extends Object implements IPlayer
Represents a proxy player who is connected remotely for the referee to use. A proxy has its own socket communication for input and output duty. Adheres to the logical protocol found in REMOTE INTERACTIONS.
